re-establish communications ``devastated by this tremendous storm.''
   ``Another FEMA team stands ready to travel to Puerto Rico as soon
as a landing site can be located, and a FEMA representative is
expected to meet with government officials in Puerto Rico today,''
Fitzwater said.
   He said requests for federal emergency aid will be reviewed and
expedited.
