political, it's not my fault. If you look at the top 10, it's quite
obvious.
   ``It was one black, one Korean, one Japanese, one hearing
impaired, one kidney transplant, and of course, Texas and Florida
were part of the top 10. It just makes you wonder.''
   Bittinger said Monday that she didn't mean her remarks to be
derogatory.
   ``It's just being blown way out of proportion,'' said Jody Bice,
Bittinger's traveling companion and business manager. ``She did not
mean it in a derogatory way. She only said what she felt. Some
people are taking it all wrong.''
